  "title": "Part-Time Admin Assistant",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Part-Time Admin Assistant (3 months Contract)</strong></u></p>\n<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Support reception desk operations</li>\n  <li>Provide administrative support to the management team</li>\n  <li>Assist with invoice processing and run simple reports</li>\n  <li>Manage the office pantry and storage space</li>\n  <li>Filing of documents and records</li>\n  <li>Assist in the packing and preparation of packages</li>\n  <li>Handle claims and timesheets</li>\n  <li>Perform ad hoc duties and any other HR matters as assigned</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum GCE 'O' Level</li>\n  <li>Ability to work independently</li>\n  <li>Microsoft Office Proficiency: Strong skills in Word, Excel, and Outlook</li>\n  <li>Basic knowledge in simple accounting (Accounts Receivable/Accounts Payable - AR/AP)</li>\n  <li>Preferably residing in Central or West areas</li>\n  <li>Available 2–3 times per week, approximately 4 hours per day</li>\n</ul>\n<p>📲 Contact us on WhatsApp at 93387787 for a quick arrangement!</p>\n<p><br></p>",
